<table width="auto"  border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tr><td colspan=3>House Bill/Resolution NO. <b>HB05043</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>FULL TITLE : AN ACT AMENDING REPUBLIC ACT NO. 7160, ALSO KNOWN AS THE LOCAL GOVERNMENT CODE, ON THE LEVEL OF THE POSITION OF SECRETARY TO THE SANGGUNIAN</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>ABSTRACT : Amends Section 469 of R.A.NO.7160 to read as follows: There shall be a secretary to the Sanggunian who shall be a career official with the rank and salary (equal) of a head of department or office. Places therefore the said position to the level of a local government department head.</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>PRINCIPAL AUTHOR/S : <b>GARCIA, GWENDOLYN F.</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>DATE FILED : 2017-02-14</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>SIGNIFICANCE: NATIONAL</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3><b>ACTIONS TAKEN BY THE COMMITTEE ON RULES</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>REFERRAL TO THE COMMITTEE ON LOCAL GOVERNMENT ON 2017-02-21</td></tr></table>